Dr. Ronachai considers each case very carefully and gives patients a clear idea of their results before doing the sugrery. Some of the procedures are: Blepharoplasty Abdominoplasty Brachioplasty Breast lifts and reduction Breast enlargements Facelifts Dermabrasion Mid face lift Forehead lift Rhinoplasty Liposuction Accu lift Vaser Hi Def Dr. Ronchai was the first plastic surgeon in Thailand that introduced the VASER hi definition and his techniques and reputation exceeds him.
